cff-version: "1.2.0"
type: software
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
title: "webKinPred: Open Kinetics Predictor"
abstract: >-
  Open Kinetics Predictor is a web interface and API for predicting enzyme
  kinetic parameters (kcat and KM) from protein sequences and substrate SMILES.
  It integrates multiple published machine learning and deep learning prediction
  engines behind a unified asynchronous job API.
